8) We want Total Sales By Month & Category

We have 5 Categories & 6 Months so the Output Rows will be 30


—> First we will Extract the Months from the Sale Date Column By Using Below Command [Y means 2025, y means 25, & M means Month in Words, m means 12]

SELECT DISTINCT DATE_FORMAT(sale_date, ‘%Y-%m’) FROM sales


SELECT DATE_FORMAT(sale_date,’%Y-%m’) AS sale_month, category, SUM(amount) AS total_sales
