9) We want Total Sales By Store Location Where Total Sales Exceeds 1 Million    [Example of HAVING]

Note - If we want to Apply Filter on Aggregation Like SUM, COUNT, MIN, MAX, AVG Then we will Use “HAVING”


SELECT store_location, SUM(amount) AS total_sales
FROM sales
GROUP BY store_location;
HAVING total_sales >=1000000



Output - 

+----------------+-------------+
| store_location | total_sales |
+----------------+-------------+
| New York       |  1022916.18 |
| Los Angeles    |  1028429.01 |
